name: VIP Pass
description:
The Very Important Pizzas (VIP) Pass is the ultimate Access Pass for all your Pizza needs. This Utility NFT includes the following Benefits (but not limited to):
    
    🍹 Free Mint Drink (1x Free Mint for the upcoming Collection)
    
    🧴 Whitelist Sauce (Additional Whitelist to share with a friend)
    
    🎁 Airdrop Pass (Receive all future Pizza drops)

    🍕 Custom Pizzas (Mint your very own custom Pizza creation)
    
    🎰 Pizza Raffles (Win HOLDER exclusive prizes)
    
    Become an early supporter and let's grow together! 🚀
